    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As I’m to my spirit turning, and from my soul I flee,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I enjoy His sweet anointing within me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He is moving and He’s spreading, deep in my very being,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As His presence fills me with delight and cheer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through failures and temptations, anxieties and griefs,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He is listening to my calling and my pleas."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He brings rest to all my burdens, and peace to all my strife,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And as grace He comes to fill me with His life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s no longer I who’s living, but Christ who lives in me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am mingled as one spirit with my Lord."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As He strengthens me with power, into my inner man"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I can live according to His rule within."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He fills me with His fullness; I day to day apply"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the riches of the Spirit’s life-supply."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He is witnessing within me: I am a son of God."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I express Him in my walk in daily life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I enjoy His full salvation, and grow organically;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will bring me unto sonship in His life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now from glory unto glory, He is transforming me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through the Spirit’s sealing I conformed will be."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When fully saturated, our being tripartite"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
